{"tid":896254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美27歲男救助了一位遭到暴力的女性 :《我的英雄學院》的影響","createTime":"2018-11-10T00:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T12:04:10.000Z","uid":25345,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5005713df5766bf85c244aaf2296aa01f16aaf5b","tid":896254,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/10/eKBHDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2FeKBHDi.jpg&h=52fd6630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/10/Ac25Gs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2FAc25Gs.jpg&h=1664a7a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/10/1d7r52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F1d7r52.jpg&h=ee5bab18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　日前，遊俠筆者曾為大家報導過，美國加利福尼亞的一位27歲《我的英雄學院》粉絲不顧個人安危與歹徒搏鬥，救助了一位遭到暴力的女性。這一行為獲得了網友們的大力讚揚。現在這位粉絲已經傷癒出院，在家中進行康複。近日，他收穫了一份特殊獎勵，北美髮行商Funimation決定將這位英雄加入《龍珠》最新劇場版的製作陣容中，他將作為配音演員參與劇場版《龍珠超：布羅利》的英文配音工作。一起來看看吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　這位見義勇為的《我的英雄學院》粉絲是美國加利福尼亞當地27歲的音樂家Blaine Hodge，為救女子身體多處被砍傷，而之所以他會這樣做，是因為受到了動畫《我的英雄學院》的影響。"},{"pid":"19024ec32cf9fd91e9a3216d51964e3a9662dcb7","tid":896254,"uid":170867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:18:07.000Z","msg":"One for all <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eca79837569edbf4fab1a31720422a4ff44f972","tid":896254,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19024ec32cf9fd91e9a3216d51964e3a9662dcb7","tid":896254,"uid":170867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:18:07.000Z","msg":"One for all <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif